title: Mother Goose
description: Nine illustrations of nursery rhymes with lines from rhymes written below. Includes "Baa, baa black sheep", "Mary, Mary quite contrary" and "Hark, hark the dogs do bark" among others. The first letter of each rhyme is printed in large red caps. Printed in yellow, blue, red, green and black on a white ground. Printed in selvedge: "An Exclusive Schumacher Hand Print".
name: Sidewall
